{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"twirl-support\">\n<h1>Twirl Support</h1>\n<p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/spray/twirl\">Twirl</a> complements <em>spray</em> with templating support.</p>\n<p>The <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/spray/spray/blob/v1.1-M7/spray-httpx/src/main/scala/spray/httpx/TwirlSupport.scala\">TwirlSupport</a> trait provides the tiny glue layer required for being able to use twirl templates directly in\n<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../spray-routing/#spray-routing\"><em>spray-routing</em></a> routes and <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../request-building/#requestbuilding\"><em>request building</em></a>.</p>\n<p>Simply mix in the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">TwirlSupport</span></tt> trait or <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">import</span> <span class=\"pre\">spray.httpx.TwirlSupport._</span></tt>.</p>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"first admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p class=\"last\">Since <em>spray-httpx</em> only comes with an optional dependency on <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/spray/twirl\">twirl</a> you still have to add it to your\nproject yourself. Check the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/spray/twirl\">twirl</a> documentation for information on how to do this.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"admonition-side-note admonition\">\n<p class=\"first admonition-title\">Side Note</p>\n<p class=\"last\">This site, for example, makes use of twirl-templates and TwirlSupport for serving all of its <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/spray/spray/tree/master/site/src/main/twirl\">pages</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": false, "title": "Twirl Support", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-httpx/twirl-support", "next": {"link": "../../spray-io/", "title": "spray-io"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-io/index", "spray-io", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-httpx/lift-json-support", "lift-json Support", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../", "title": "spray-httpx"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Twirl Support</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../lift-json-support/", "title": "lift-json Support"}, "metatags": ""}